91
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:48,670
- Yu─
- That's right!

92
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:51,130
Yu Seung Seok!

93
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:58,490
Wow, what a total sucker.

94
00:06:58,490 --> 00:07:02,760
Yes, I'm a total sucker. I am!

95
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:08,340
