108
00:08:17,064 --> 00:08:18,688
Seo Jae Yun.

109
00:08:19,890 --> 00:08:21,556
Seo Jae Yun.

110
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:25,240
Are you sleeping?

111
00:08:26,930 --> 00:08:29,387
