134
00:10:15,850 --> 00:10:20,270
I doubt it. Why would people call the cat a very intelligent animal?

135
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:22,910
They'll remember every grateful moment with you.

136
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,980
They'll remember it.

137
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:29,540
