142
00:11:04,350 --> 00:11:05,920
No, no.

143
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:11,130
He said he can't remember anything when he drinks, so let's trust his words.

144
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,800
What are you trusting?

145
00:11:21,810 --> 00:11:25,580
- Don't you think it's not okay?
- Pardon?

146
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:30,095
I got late to work because of you. You made me drink a ton last night.

147
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:35,430
