153
00:11:58,290 --> 00:12:02,800
I had an urgent task to take care of this morning.

154
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:05,790
Then I'll go back to work now.

155
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:07,580
Seo Jae Yun.

156
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:09,820
Yes?

157
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:13,240
Didn't you forget something?

158
00:12:15,730 --> 00:12:17,380
Your memory is a bit...

159
00:12:17,380 --> 00:12:20,790
What? What about my memory?

160
00:12:54,780 --> 00:12:56,680
Your coffee.

161
00:12:56,680 --> 00:13:01,050
Right, thank you.

162
00:13:01,050 --> 00:13:03,010
Right, my coffee.

163
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:17,250
[Report on business items of the New Business Planning Team]

164
00:13:26,930 --> 00:13:29,910
