168
00:13:50,090 --> 00:13:53,410
- Jae Yun.
- Yes?

169
00:13:53,410 --> 00:13:57,240
I just sent you a file to your email address. Can you put that on the screen?

170
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,927
Yes, Sir.

171
00:14:07,300 --> 00:14:09,870
