190
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:38,590
- It's Employee Seo Jae Yun's idea.
- Really?

191
00:15:38,590 --> 00:15:40,330
Daebak.

192
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:45,170
I saw Seo Jae Yun's portfolio that he submitted when he got into this company,

193
00:15:45,170 --> 00:15:47,600
