196
00:15:56,480 --> 00:16:02,550
No matter how hard we try, we can't catch up with the fresh ideas of the young employees.

197
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:08,060
Jae Yun, why didn't you share this idea until now?

198
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:13,030
